<div class="container mt-4">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: May 4, 2025</p>
    <p>
        Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our web application.
    </p>

    <h4>1. Information We Collect</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> When you register, we collect your username, email, and a password hash for authentication.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We may collect data on how you interact with our services (e.g., songs played, playlists created) for analytics and improving user experience.</li>
        <li><strong>Files:</strong> Any audio files you upload are stored in our secure storage and processed solely to provide music playback.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>To provide, maintain, and improve our services.</li>
        <li>To authenticate users and secure your account.</li>
        <li>To personalize your experience, such as suggesting playlists.</li>
        <li>To comply with legal obligations and protect against fraud.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>3. Cookies and Tracking</h4>
    <p>
        We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your experience. You can manage cookie preferences in your browser settings.
    </p>

    <h4>4. Third-Party Services</h4>
    <p>
        We do not share your personal data with third parties except for hosting (e.g., cloud storage) and analytics providers. Any such service is GDPR compliant.
    </p>

    <h4>5. Data Security</h4>
    <p>
        We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data. However, no system is 100% secure; please use strong passwords and enable multi-factor authentication where possible.
    </p>

    <h4>6. Children’s Privacy</h4>
    <p>
        Our services are not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from minors.
    </p>

    <h4>7. Changes to This Policy</h4>
    <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of significant changes via email or an in-app notification.
    </p>

    <h4>8. Contact Us</h4>
    <p>
        If you have questions or concerns about this policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@musicapp.com">privacy@musicapp.com</a>.
    </p>
</div>
